Rating: 3
I was really pleased with how this recipe turned out. It makes way more than two servings - more like 4-5! We added garlic to the onions when sauteeing them, and precooked the chicken for safety's sake. Added flour-roux to the final mixture to thicken it up a bit, and used half rosemary, half thyme. Needed salt, and time for the flavors to infuse, but it turned out great! Will definitely make this one again.

